#: ../../polymorphism.md:1
msgid "Polymorphic arguments"
msgstr "多态参数"

#: ../../polymorphism.md:3
msgid "Input polymorphism"
msgstr "输入多态"

#: ../../polymorphism.md:5
msgid "*New in Koffi 2.1*"
msgstr "*Koffi 2.1引入*"

#: ../../polymorphism.md:7
msgid ""
"Many C functions use `void *` parameters in order to pass polymorphic "
"objects and arrays, meaning that the data format changes can change "
"depending on one other argument, or on some kind of struct tag member."
msgstr ""
"许多C函数使用`void *`参数来传入多态的对象或数组, 意味着数据格式会随着某个其它参数, 或是某种类型的结构体标签成员变化而变化."

#: ../../polymorphism.md:9
msgid "Koffi provides two features to deal with this:"
msgstr "Koffi提供了两个功能来处理这种情况:"

#: ../../polymorphism.md:11
msgid ""
"Buffers and typed JS arrays can be used as values in place everywhere a "
"pointer is expected. See [dynamic arrays](pointers.md#array-pointers-"
"dynamic-arrays) for more information, for input or output."
msgstr ""
"Buffer和TypedArray可以用在任何需要指针的地方. 参见[动态数组](pointers.md#array-pointers-dynamic-arrays)以获取更多信息, 包括输入和输出."

#: ../../polymorphism.md:12
msgid ""
"You can use `koffi.as(value, type)` to tell Koffi what kind of type is "
"actually expected."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用`koffi.as(value, type)`来告诉Koffi到底应当是什么类型."

#: ../../polymorphism.md:14
msgid ""
"The example below shows the use of `koffi.as()` to read the header of a "
"PNG file with `fread()`."
msgstr ""
"下面的例子展示了使用`fread()`和`koffi.as()`来读取一个PNG文件的文件头."

#: ../../polymorphism.md:66
msgid "Output buffers"
msgstr "输出Buffer"

#: ../../polymorphism.md:68
msgid "*New in Koffi 2.3*"
msgstr "*Koffi 2.3引入*"

#: ../../polymorphism.md:70
msgid ""
"You can use buffers and typed arrays for output (and input/output) "
"pointer parameters. Simply pass the buffer as an argument and the native "
"function will receive a pointer to its contents."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用Buffer和TypedArray作为输出(以及输入/输出)指针参数. "
"简单的传入Buffer作为参数然后原生函数就会接收到一个指向其内容的指针."

#: ../../polymorphism.md:72
msgid ""
"Once the native function returns, you can decode the content with "
"`koffi.decode(value, type)` as in the following example:"
msgstr ""
"一旦原生函数返回, 你可以通过`koffi.decode(value, type)`来像如下示例解码内容:"

#: ../../polymorphism.md:108
msgid ""
"See [pointer arguments](callbacks.md#decoding-pointer-arguments) for "
"another example with the decode function."
msgstr ""
"参见[指针参数](callbacks.md#decoding-pointer-arguments)以获取其它关于解码函数的示例."
